movie.title: Blood and Steel, Cedar Crest Country Club
movie.title_english: Blood and Steel, Cedar Crest Country Club
movie.title_long: Blood and Steel, Cedar Crest Country Club (2017)
movie.description_intro: In the middle of nowhere lived an unexpected piece of skateboarding and punk music history. "The Crest"..a skateboarding mecca of the 80's, a veritable metal monolith, tucked away on a country club in the suburbs of the nation's Capital. It was a place of pure unadulterated expressionist freedom where cutting edge skateboarding and punk rock music collided and made history. Professional skaters and legendary bands, 11 gauge steel and, of course, blood. "Blood and Steel: Cedar Crest Country Club" is the story of a one of a kind skateboarding playground that attracted skaters and bands from all over to come experience what became known simply as, "The Crest".

movies.title: Jazz: The Only Way of Life
movies.title_english: Jazz: The Only Way of Life
movies.title_long: Jazz: The Only Way of Life (2017)
movies.summary: Dizzy Gillespie is one of the major figures of the 20th Century's music scene. Everything was once said or written about this genius musician, founder of the Bebop. Whereas his public life is known from most, many ignore about the modest side of his character and the story of his long and deep friendship with a man rather unknown from the general public, the Swiss engineer Jacques Muyal. Through previously unrevealed archives as well as musical extracts, this documentary explores the story of the friendship between a genius trumpeter and a man crazy about Jazz.

movies.title: The Great Fortune
movies.summary: Mirco Kuball: an ultra-wealthy, flamboyant, sophisticated and outspoken man who just happens to have down's syndrome. This touching film explores an unexpected life. It moves through the castle where he lives; the massage parlours and restaurants where he's indulged; and the theatre where he performs. But, beneath the opulent showman, lies a man like any other, who realises that beyond shelter, food, and companionship, nothing else counts.

movies.title: Out of Many, One
movies.summary: The United States has long offered a promise of opportunity and safety to arriving immigrants - The American Dream. However, currently facing a time of deep political, social, and cultural divide, immigration has become a divisive issue.
